      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私って怖いんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "いきなりどうしたんだ？　何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 4.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "それが……SNSに「一ノ瀬怜は性格がきつくて\n怒ると怖そう」って書かれていたんです",
      "startTime": 14.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "それくらいならたまに見かけるので\n気にしないようにしてるんですが、今回は……",
      "startTime": 20.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "「サニピのメンバーも一ノ瀬怜を怖がって\nいつも気を遣っていそう」とまで書かれていて……",
      "startTime": 27.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "私ってそんなに怖そうに見えますか？",
      "startTime": 32.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜はクールで気が強いイメージがあるから\nきつい印象を持たれやすいのかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 39.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなが思ってるほど私はクールじゃありません\n現に今もこうして気にしてるんですから",
      "startTime": 46.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "確かにSNSの書き込みを見て一喜一憂するのは\nクールとは言えないな",
      "startTime": 54.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "もう……何がおかしいんですか？",
      "startTime": 56.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、クールな印象が強い怜も、素顔は\n些細なことで思い悩む可愛い女の子なんだと思ってね",
      "startTime": 63.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "か、可愛くなんてありません！　可愛いっていうのは\nさくらや千紗みたいな子のことです",
      "startTime": 72.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "私はさくらみたいに天真爛漫に笑えないし\n千紗みたいに守りたくなる笑顔も出来ませんから",
      "startTime": 79.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな？　分かり辛いだけで\n怜にも可愛いところは沢山あると思うが……",
      "startTime": 85.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……。{user}さんと話してると\n真面目に悩んでるのがバカらしく思えてきました",
      "startTime": 94.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それでいいんじゃないか？　ネットの書き込みも\nそんなに深刻に考えずに、気楽に聞き流せばいいんだ",
      "startTime": 101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "それもそうですね……\nなんだか話を聞いてもらったら少し気が楽になりました",
      "startTime": 108.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "役に立てたのなら良かった\nこれからも困ったことがあればいつでも相談してくれ",
      "startTime": 115.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 119.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nやっぱり私って怖いんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 123.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　昨日は納得してなかったか？\n今度はどうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 130.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "実は、ダンスレッスン中の千紗と雫に\n強い口調でダメ出しをしてしまったんです",
      "startTime": 136.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "二人とももっと踊れるはずなのに\n現状で満足しているように見えて、つい……",
      "startTime": 142.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "最初は普通のアドバイスだったんです\nでもだんだんヒートアップして口調がきつくなって……",
      "startTime": 150.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "気付いた時には二人ともチワワみたいに\nブルブル震えて怯えていたんです",
      "startTime": 158.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "正論を言ってるだけで責めてるつもりはなかったのに\n……私ってそんなに怖いんでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 165.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "怜に叱られて二人が怯えるのはよくあることじゃないか\n多分、千紗と雫もそれほど気にしていないと思うぞ",
      "startTime": 174.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "私がいつも怖がらせてるみたいに言わないで下さい\nそりゃあ今までも似たようなことはありましたけど……",
      "startTime": 182.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei019.m4a",
      "text": "今回は自分でも厳しく言い過ぎた気がして……\nなんとなく顔を合わせ辛いんです",
      "startTime": 190.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei020.m4a",
      "text": "今夜はライブバトルがあるので、それまでに\n二人とちゃんと話したいと思ってるんですけど……",
      "startTime": 196.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、話すなら早い方がいい\n大丈夫、ちゃんと話せば二人とも分かってくれるさ",
      "startTime": 202.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei021.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですね。{user}さんを信じて\n二人に話しかけてみます",
      "startTime": 210.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その夜、ライブバトル終了後",
      "startTime": 213.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei022.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……",
      "startTime": 216.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "表情が暗いな……\nひょっとして千紗達と話せなかったのか？",
      "startTime": 221.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei023.m4a",
      "text": "はい……ライブは問題なく終わったんですが\n結局、千紗と雫とはぎくしゃくしたままで……",
      "startTime": 229.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei024.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、ライブ後の物販をみんなで手伝ったんですけど\nその様子を見た人がSNSに書き込みしたらしくて……",
      "startTime": 239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei025.m4a",
      "text": "「怜ちゃんは目が笑ってなくて怖かった」とか\n「怖い顔で二人を睨みつけていた」とか書かれたんです",
      "startTime": 247.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
