      "text": "それで遠目に見ていただけなのに\n睨みつけていたなんて言われて……",
      "startTime": 265.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そんな勘違いされるのも\n怜が持つイメージの影響かもしれないな",
      "startTime": 270.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei028.m4a",
      "text": "またそれですか。勝手なイメージで「顔が怖い」とか\n「視線で人を消せそう」とか言われるのは心外です",
      "startTime": 279.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そこまでは言ってないと思うが……\nとりあえず千紗と雫とはちゃんと話し合った方がいい",
      "startTime": 286.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei029.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよね……\n分かりました。明日こそ、二人に話しかけてみます！",
      "startTime": 293.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-rei030.m4a",
      "text": "……って、ライブ前もそう言って\n話しかけられなかったんですけど……",
      "startTime": 300.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_04_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "一人で話すのが不安なら俺が間に入ろうか？",
      "startTime": 303.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
